{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-content-js","path":"/contact","result":{"data":{"contentfulPage":{"title":"Contact us","slug":"contact","contentful_id":"5duGdghzwKR7IkuQd1gWmF","returnLinkTitle":null,"returnLinkUrl":null,"enableToc":null,"body":{"childMarkdownRemark":{"html":"<p><strong>As of March 31st, 2021, we cannot promise to respond to any messages.</strong> We expect to be shut down altogether by the end of May 2021.</p>\n<h2 id=\"before-you-contact-us\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#before-you-contact-us\" aria-label=\"before you contact us permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Before you contact us</h2>\n<p>If you’d like to read about our reasons for ceasing data collection, please read the following explanations.  </p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://covidtracking.com/analysis-updates/covid-tracking-project-end-march-7\">It’s Time: The COVID Tracking Project Will Soon Come to an End</a>, 2/1/21</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://covidtracking.com/analysis-updates/giving-thanks-and-looking-ahead-our-data-collection-work-is-done\">Giving Thanks and Looking Ahead</a>, 3/8/21</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://covidtracking.com/analysis-updates/the-decisions-we-made\">The Decisions We Made</a>, 3/31/21</li>\n</ul>\n<p>If you’d like to learn how to get along without The COVID Tracking Project, you might be interested in the following guides to federal data.</p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://covidtracking.com/analysis-updates/federal-covid-data-101-how-to-find-data\">Federal COVID Data 101</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://covidtracking.com/analysis-updates/simple-covid-data\">Where to Find Simple COVID-19 Data for the US</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://covidtracking.com/about-data/data-summary\">All Datasets</a> from CTP with comparable federal data listed</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://covidtracking.com/about-data/federal-resources\">Federal Resources</a></li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"government-correspondence\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#government-correspondence\" aria-label=\"government correspondence permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Government correspondence</h2>\n<p>If you represent or are employed by a county, state, or federal government body and have a question or concern about the data we compiled, you can write <a href=\"mailto:government@covidtracking.com\">government@covidtracking.com</a>.</p>\n<h2 id=\"media-inquiries\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#media-inquiries\" aria-label=\"media inquiries permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Media inquiries</h2>\n<p>If you are a journalist and would like an on-the-record quote for an article or would like to interview someone from The COVID Tracking Project, you can write <a href=\"mailto:media-inquiries@covidtracking.com\">media-inquiries@covidtracking.com</a>.</p>\n<h2 id=\"general-questions-and-comments\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#general-questions-and-comments\" aria-label=\"general questions and comments permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>General questions and comments</h2>\n<p>If you have a general question or comment, you can write <a href=\"mailto:contact@covidtracking.com\">contact@covidtracking.com</a>. </p>\n<h2 id=\"tell-us-what-our-work-meant-to-you\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#tell-us-what-our-work-meant-to-you\" aria-label=\"tell us what our work meant to you permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Tell us what our work meant to you</h2>\n<p>We are collecting stories about our impact and would love to <a href=\"https://covidtracking.com/about/track-impact\">hear yours</a>.</p>","headings":[{"id":"before-you-contact-us","value":"Before you contact us","depth":2},{"id":"government-correspondence","value":"Government correspondence","depth":2},{"id":"media-inquiries","value":"Media inquiries","depth":2},{"id":"general-questions-and-comments","value":"General questions and comments","depth":2},{"id":"tell-us-what-our-work-meant-to-you","value":"Tell us what our work meant to you","depth":2}]}},"socialCard":null}},"pageContext":{"id":"916cb06f-e7fa-58f0-a369-58260890b9b0","slug":"contact","latestDate":"2021-03-07","sevenDaysAgo":"2021-02-28","fourteenDaysAgo":"2021-02-21","twentyEightDaysAgo":"2021-02-07","ninetyDaysAgo":"2020-12-07"}},"staticQueryHashes":["1039529027","3565063634","3649515864","4121435362","775579208"]}